sdef

Extract the synthesis definition (sdef) from the argument using the appropriate means Accepts at least the following synthdef args types: * synths * synthdefs * imported-synthdefs * keyword (will look up the synthdef with the name matching keyword in the default SuperCollider synthdef directory * string (will look up the synthdef with a path matching string) * URL (will look up the synthdef with URL)

  * string (will look up the synthdef with a path matching string)
